      <title>Alpine Immune 正在权衡收购兴趣后的选择</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/alpine-immune-is-said-to-weigh-options-after-takeover-interest</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，Alpine Immune Sciences Inc. 是一家临床阶段的生物技术公司，正在开发一种治疗炎症性肾病的药物，该公司正在权衡各种选择，包括在吸引收购兴趣后可能进行出售。该股涨幅高达 17%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/alpine-immune-is-said-to-weigh-options-after-takeover-interest</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 16:33:14 GMT</pubDate>
